ygData.messageBody:
Hello friends,
I am Lita on Server Bertolouxxis (sp) and I am a Bi fem from Miami Florida. I love rp and have been involved in many games over the years. I have several chars, all female, on the server. I would love to join with some of you in adverntures of this realm. Even more, it would be great to start on a new server somewhere, and join as a guild. I do not have the time or desire to be a leader but I can be a very faithful and submisive follower. I am currently a Ranger and a Druid, but will be what ever is needed if we form together in a new world......
